basics.name: Keanu Robles
basics.label: IT Specialist
basics.summary: From 2013 - 2017, I studied at the University of Hawaii at Manoa and recieved a Bachelor of Science in Computer Engineering. My interests range from computer architecture and design, to software engineering and mobile development.

work.company: University of Hawai'i Information Technology Services
highlights: Assess, evaluate, and resolve issues for UH customers regarding hardware, software, network, and servers
Provide in-depth troubleshooting of account issues associated with the Banner Student Information System (SIS) and other integrated systems
Independently research, provide valid detailed and accurate testing results, and write up documentation of new applications or new versions of software
Provide supervision, guidance, and direction to the ITS Help Desk students in their execution of job-related tasks
